---
title: Seared Barramundi and Horseradish Sauce with a Crisp Apple Salad
description: When a creamy horseradish sauce is involved, you know you’re in for a fun and feisty recipe, and this dish is no exception! The kickin’ condiment provides the perfect contrast to flaky barramundi, crispy roasted potatoes, and a bright, apple-studded salad. The best part? It only takes 35 minutes for this stunning dish to land on your table.
